A man has been arrested in connection with the murder of Stephen McGinlay in Glasgow. Man, 20, arrested in Woodside murder probe A man has been arrested in connection with the murder of Stephen McGinlay in Glasgow.Police said a 20-year-old was being held following the death of Mr McGinlay, 26, who was attacked in the Woodside area on October 2.He died in hospital several days later.The suspect is expected to appear at Glasgow Sheriff Court tomorrow. 